Package: togoid
Type: Package
Title: R Library for Biological Database ID Conversion and Annotation
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("DBCLS", email = "noreply@dbcls.jp", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: R library and CLI tool for biological database ID conversion and
    annotation using TogoID (https://togoid.dbcls.jp/). Provides functions for
    converting IDs between biological databases, retrieving annotations, and
    converting labels to IDs.
